1
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,580
=Reincarnated Love=

2
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:42,700
=Episode 3=

3
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:45,400
Let go of me.

4
00:00:46,960 --> 00:00:47,800
You wretch.

5
00:00:48,070 --> 00:00:48,910
Let go of me.

6
00:00:49,110 --> 00:00:50,790
You did such a disgraceful thing.

7
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:53,240
How am I supposed to answer
your father?

8
00:00:53,710 --> 00:00:55,350
Forgive me for speaking bluntly.

9
00:00:55,390 --> 00:00:56,670
As a lady,

10
00:00:56,670 --> 00:00:57,670
you're pregnant.

11
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:59,920
That'll disgrace the entire family.

12
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,960
You two truly don't know

13
00:01:04,070 --> 00:01:06,350
how I became pregnant?

14
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:07,760
Insolent thing.

15
00:01:08,230 --> 00:01:09,710
You're pregnant,

16
00:01:10,070 --> 00:01:11,560
yet you speak rudely to your elders

17
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:12,760
and slander your cousin.

18
00:01:12,950 --> 00:01:14,280
Force the medicine on her.

19
00:01:14,710 --> 00:01:15,976
Get rid of the kid in her belly.

20
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:20,840
Let go of me!

21
00:01:21,230 --> 00:01:22,510
I'd like to see who dares.

22
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,430
Are you okay?

23
00:01:40,510 --> 00:01:41,350
I'm fine.

24
00:01:42,350 --> 00:01:43,640
Mr. Huo, what do you mean?

25
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:46,113
I want to see who dares touch her.

26
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:47,680
Mr. Huo,

27
00:01:48,350 --> 00:01:49,840
even as the Duke's son,

28
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:52,510
you have no right to barge in here

29
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,150
and interfere with our family affairs.

30
00:01:54,430 --> 00:01:56,350
She carries my child.

31
00:01:56,790 --> 00:01:58,120
Do you think I have the right?

32
00:02:00,140 --> 00:02:01,040
Mr. Huo,

33
00:02:01,070 --> 00:02:02,310
you must've made a mistake.

34
00:02:16,340 --> 00:02:17,940
(Betrothal Letter)

35
00:02:17,951 --> 00:02:19,297
The formal rites are all prepared.

36
00:02:19,590 --> 00:02:20,430
In three days,

37
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,360
I'll marry Miss Jiang.

38
00:02:26,340 --> 00:02:27,420
(Betrothal Letter)

39
00:02:28,750 --> 00:02:30,030
During this time,

40
00:02:30,190 --> 00:02:32,870
if anything happens to my wife

41
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:33,910
or the child in her belly,

42
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,400
I wonder if Mr. Jiang

43
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:39,150
can bear the responsibility.

44
00:03:02,870 --> 00:03:04,710
Milady, Mr. Lu is here.

45
00:03:13,750 --> 00:03:14,590
Yuan,

46
00:03:15,030 --> 00:03:16,630
did Yanzhi force you

47
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:17,960
to marry him?

48
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,000
He never forced me.

49
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:26,630
I knew it.

50
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,020
With your temperament,

51
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:29,030
you'd never do this.

52
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,200
Ruoli.

53
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:37,240
I'll soon marry Mr. Huo

54
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:39,430
and be your sister-in-law.

55
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:41,280
I'll always remember

56
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:42,590
our bond

57
00:03:43,910 --> 00:03:45,240
in my heart.

58
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:48,280
Are you giving up on me

59
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:51,710
because he's the Duke's legitimate son?

60
00:03:53,430 --> 00:03:54,280
Yunzhou,

61
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:57,630
I wish you to find a good match soon.

62
00:04:00,630 --> 00:04:01,470
Farewell.

63
00:04:02,030 --> 00:04:02,870
Yuan,

64
00:04:04,210 --> 00:04:05,360
whenever

65
00:04:06,310 --> 00:04:07,470
you need me,

66
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:09,190
I'll always be there.

67
00:04:17,510 --> 00:04:18,830
(I'm sorry, Yunzhou.)

68
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,240
(I have to avenge my father.)

69
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:25,190
(Forgive me for not indulging in love.)

70
00:04:32,100 --> 00:04:44,100
(Joy)

71
00:04:45,550 --> 00:04:48,080
♪Gentle rain seeps into the deep night♪

72
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:50,280
♪Stirring the jasmine from slumber♪

73
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:54,240
♪Two swallows nest upon the beam♪

74
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:56,610
♪Bringing fresh mud for the home♪

75
00:04:56,610 --> 00:04:57,970
(Joy)

76
00:04:57,970 --> 00:05:00,370
♪Gazing afar at the roadside
that I once knew♪

77
00:05:00,370 --> 00:05:03,450
♪Lush grass swayed in abundance♪

78
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:08,720
♪Though beauty abounds,
it answered not your call♪

79
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:12,640
♪A sudden gust stirs in the night♪

80
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:15,800
♪The pond ripples in gentle waves♪

81
00:05:16,420 --> 00:05:19,230
♪Most afraid
when the full moon turns to fear♪

82
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,430
Why are you hiding?

83
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:23,000
♪That same gentle smile♪

84
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,390
Since you used my name,

85
00:05:25,310 --> 00:05:26,810
you should at least pay some interest.

86
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:31,070
Please behave yourself.

87
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,680
Why are you so flustered?

88
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,480
That day,

89
00:05:36,363 --> 00:05:37,430
weren't you very proactive?

90
00:05:37,430 --> 00:05:39,190
♪Together from dawn till dusk♪

91
00:05:39,190 --> 00:05:41,920
♪Who'd think parting comes so easily♪

92
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:45,430
♪Yet reunion hardly comes by♪

93
00:05:45,430 --> 00:05:48,130
♪You always cheer me up♪

94
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,760
Jiang Ruoli,

95
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,000
wake up.

96
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:14,360
Why do you keep appearing in my dreams?

97
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,760
Who are you?

98
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,440
Huo Linchuan.

99
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,920
Huo Linchuan?

100
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,600
Are you crazy?

101
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,800
Listen, Huo Linchuan.

102
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:37,000
I dreamed
that you were assassinated and died.

103
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:40,480
My dreams can foresee the future.

104
00:06:42,270 --> 00:06:44,950
(In my previous life,
she mentioned Wuyou Ferry.)

105
00:06:45,830 --> 00:06:46,670
(Could her dreams)

106
00:06:47,190 --> 00:06:48,920
(really foresee the future?)

107
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:52,023
I can change your fate of death.

108
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:53,830
But I have one condition.

109
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:55,270
What condition?

110
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,360
Protect my family's lives.

111
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,750
Using our lives as the wager,

112
00:07:02,870 --> 00:07:04,270
Jiang Ruoli, you are ruthless.

113
00:07:05,270 --> 00:07:06,110
I want you

114
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,200
to marry me.

115
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,320
Fine.

116
00:07:16,590 --> 00:07:17,440
Physician Zhang.

117
00:07:17,450 --> 00:07:18,300
Milady,

118
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:19,600
this won't do.

119
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:22,070
Your parents were so kind to my family.

120
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:25,190
Now that you need my help,

121
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,630
I'll naturally do my utmost to assist.

122
00:07:29,070 --> 00:07:30,390
Thank you, Physician Zhang.

123
00:07:31,310 --> 00:07:33,430
Lady Ruoli's pulse
is smooth and flowing,

124
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:34,723
like pearls rolling on a plate.

125
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:37,000
This is indeed a pregnancy pulse.

126
00:07:52,630 --> 00:07:54,830
I didn't expect you to be so strong.

127
00:08:04,309 --> 00:08:05,535
The ceremony wasn't completed.

128
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,120
Drink this nuptial wine.

129
00:08:07,950 --> 00:08:09,070
The nuptial wine

130
00:08:09,070 --> 00:08:10,270
is meant for a real couple.

131
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:12,040
You and I

132
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:14,630
are merely allies with mutual interests.

133
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:17,590
Once everything is settled,

134
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:21,040
we will go our separate ways.

135
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,560
What a fine saying.

136
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:25,720
Go our separate ways.

137
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,120
Then I wish my wife...

138
00:08:46,790 --> 00:08:47,630
No.

139
00:08:48,870 --> 00:08:49,750
I wish my ally

140
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:51,910
peaceful sleep every night

141
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,273
and no dreams of the past.

142
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:56,360
I'll sleep on the couch outside.

143
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,720
Rest early.

144
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,630
It's the lady's wedding day.

145
00:09:14,630 --> 00:09:15,960
Why do you look so worried?

146
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:18,870
She married alone
into this enormous mansion.

147
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,720
There is no one here to support her.

148
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,320
Tao,

149
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:27,200
you must stay alert

150
00:09:27,670 --> 00:09:29,050
and never let her fall into danger.

151
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:30,270
Do you understand?

152
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:31,320
Yes.

153
00:10:13,670 --> 00:10:14,630
Help!

154
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:44,030
♪The dream shattered♪

155
00:10:44,390 --> 00:10:46,070
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

156
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:47,320
(Ruoli,)

157
00:10:47,790 --> 00:10:49,200
(I know that in your world,)

158
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:52,320
(each life is the only life you have.)

159
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,360
(But this time)

160
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:56,080
(is my final life.)

161
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:59,240
(I must try my best to live)

162
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,840
(and protect you.)

163
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:06,430
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

164
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:08,550
♪When fate falls apart♪

165
00:11:08,950 --> 00:11:12,510
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

166
00:11:13,230 --> 00:11:14,790
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

167
00:11:15,190 --> 00:11:18,910
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

168
00:11:39,030 --> 00:11:40,550
♪The dream shattered♪

169
00:11:40,910 --> 00:11:42,590
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

170
00:11:42,590 --> 00:11:44,230
♪Like a restless soul♪

171
00:11:45,110 --> 00:11:46,670
♪How vague♪

172
00:11:47,070 --> 00:11:48,590
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

173
00:11:48,590 --> 00:11:50,830
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

174
00:11:51,630 --> 00:11:54,230
♪Love and hate entwined♪

175
00:11:54,710 --> 00:11:57,550
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

176
00:11:58,190 --> 00:12:02,950
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

177
00:12:03,550 --> 00:12:05,070
♪When fate falls apart♪

178
00:12:05,470 --> 00:12:09,030
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

179
00:12:09,750 --> 00:12:11,310
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

180
00:12:11,710 --> 00:12:15,430
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

181
00:12:16,150 --> 00:12:18,990
♪Life after life♪

182
00:12:19,470 --> 00:12:22,150
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

183
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:26,870
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

184
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:29,990
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

185
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:31,550
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

186
00:12:31,550 --> 00:12:34,670
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

187
00:12:34,750 --> 00:12:36,190
♪Now shatter apart♪

188
00:12:36,310 --> 00:12:40,070
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

189
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:43,590
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

190
00:12:43,870 --> 00:12:46,710
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

191
00:12:47,030 --> 00:12:51,430
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

192
00:12:51,670 --> 00:12:54,590
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

193
00:12:54,710 --> 00:12:59,150
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

194
00:12:59,350 --> 00:13:05,070
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

195
00:13:05,510 --> 00:13:08,230
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

196
00:13:08,470 --> 00:13:11,190
♪Sober or indulge♪

197
00:13:11,630 --> 00:13:17,630
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪
